OL,6,FThe gap between working class and
OL,7,Fmiddle class graduates accessing work-
OL,8,Frelated internships is growing,
OL,9,Fresearch suggests.
OL,11,FThe Sutton Trust said the trend is
OL,12,Fdriven by employers continuing to
OL,13,Funderpay interns, and giving
OL,14,Fopportunities to family and friends
OL,15,Frather than advertising them.
OL,17,FA poll of more than 1,200 recent
OL,18,Fgraduates, conducted by Public First
OL,19,Ffor the Sutton Trust, showed half have
OL,20,Fundertaken an internship, a growth of
OL,21,F12% since 2018.
