OL,3,CGrowing gap in access to internships,
OL,4,Cstudy suggests
OL,6,FChief executive Nick Harrison said:
OL,7,F"Internships are an increasingly
OL,8,Fcritical route into the best jobs and
OL,9,Fit's shocking that in this day and
OL,10,Fage, many employers still pay interns
OL,11,Fbelow the minimum wage, or worse,
OL,12,Fnothing at all.
OL,14,F"The Government has pledged to ban
OL,15,Funpaid internships, which is
OL,16,Fabsolutely the right thing to do.
OL,17,FClearly not all young people can get
OL,18,Fsupport from the bank of mum and dad
OL,19,Fso banning this outdated practice will
OL,20,Fhelp to level the playing field for
OL,21,Fthese valuable opportunities.
